attempts.sparql_query: PREFIX nas: <http://www.semanticdesktop.org/ontologies/2007/04/18/nas#> SELECT ?flight ?num_flight_attendants WHERE { ?flight a nas:Flight ; nas:num_flight_attendants ?num_flight_attendants . FILTER ( ?flight = 'ACA722' || ?flight = 'AAL1170' ) }
attempts.query_explanation: This SPARQL query retrieves the number of flight attendants for flights ACA722 and AAL1170. It uses the nas:Flight class to filter the results and returns the flight and its corresponding number of flight attendants.
